tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE diagnostic_information (
	diag_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_id INT,
	error_code INT,
	details JSONB,
	timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_error_codes (
	code_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	error_code VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
	error_description TEXT,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_readings (
	reading_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_id INT NOT NULL,
	reading_value DECIMAL(10,2),
	reading_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_errors (
	error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_id INT NOT NULL,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	error_code INT
)

CREATE TABLE diagnostic_logs (
	log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_id INT NOT NULL,
	log_message TEXT,
	log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE maintenance_tasks (
	task_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_id INT NOT NULL,
	task_description TEXT,
	task_status VARCHAR(20),
	assigned_technician VARCHAR(50),
	completion_date DATE
)
